        {
            "date": "2009-02-10 16:43:18", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Hi,", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "> From the bug report it's not clear to me, whether ejabberd has\n> really an upgrade problem or not.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "If this is realle the case, I\n> will put your text into the release notes, OK?", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Partly yes:", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "> 1) Back up /var/lib/ejabberd *before* upgrading.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "This is the directory contains all data for ejabberd.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Therefore it is\nalways a good idea to do a backup.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": ";", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "-) Secondly the database format has\nchanged and ejabberd will migrate tables to the new format.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "As a result\nit is not possible to downgrade again if you run into trouble with the\nnew ejabberd.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "> 2) The syntax of the configuration file changed, so it must be updated\n>    by hand.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Most users will have adapted their configuration file.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "They will have\ndefined server admins for instance.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Keeping the old configuration file\nwill result in a wrong configuration of ejabberd as some configuration\nitmes changed their name.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "> 3) The upgraded ejabberd may be unable to start up (for unknown\n>    reasons).", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I was unable to further investigate this issue due to lack of time.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I\nwas asked to try this by upgrading to lenny, but that would have\nrequired me setting up a dedicated machine.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "There has been an upload\nfixing the issue, but it seemed to fix pubsub table migration.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "As I\ndon't use pubsub I believe (but can of course not prove) that the\nproblem will still affect at least some users.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Hope this helps.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Helmut", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
